### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "zs@example.com"
}

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取章节1的定理列表（需要 token）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/theorems/chapter/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ6aGFuZ3NhbiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NjEwMzc5NSwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MTkwMTk1fQ.AqqPI9S1oZ8Jg4G-Bkzqn3BWtg1VDN5NZxPaHWG7ZxI

### 搜索定理（关键词：行列式）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/theorems/search?keyword=行列式
